author: Jorge Alonso
title: The Internet Mocks Duke With Hilarious Memes After Their Upset Loss To South Carolina
text:
Tonight, #2 seeded Duke was eliminated in an upset loss against South Carolina in the second round of the NCAA tourney. 
Of course whenever Duke loses the jokes start flying. 
Me texting every duke fan that I know…. pic.twitter.com/L7i1esGCsI 
— A. (@FreshAir_In) March 20, 2017 
Who is Duke? pic.twitter.com/2JXES0s7kk 
— Jayhawk World (@RockChalkWorld) March 20, 2017 


DUKE IS SAD pic.twitter.com/UJwXoFSiIC 
— SB Nation GIF (@SBNationGIF) March 20, 2017 
Welp, sorry Duke. pic.twitter.com/zb9OznLpT5 
— Ben Gibson (@CowboyOnPatrol) March 20, 2017 


1729: Carolinas split into 2 colonies after decades of feuding.
2017: North Carolina and South Carolina remerge over shared hatred of Duke pic.twitter.com/formotdSnd 
— Tyler Conway (@jtylerconway) March 20, 2017 
Here's a live look of every Duke fan right now pic.twitter.com/VNVPQIrbod 
— Mike Ortiz Jr. (@xOrtiz4x) March 20, 2017 


UK Wins
UL Loses
Duke Loses #BBN pic.twitter.com/wgkj3mvciq
